表格超量生产记录表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblExcessProduct')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblExcessProduct
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblExcessProduct */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblExcessProduct (
ID int not null,
MachineNo varchar(20) null,
DispatchNo varchar(50) null,
flag smallint null,
CreateDate datetime null,
constraint PK_TBLEXCESSPRODUCT primary key (ID)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'超量生产记录',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblExcessProduct'
go
